character.name: Gong Jun
character.description: Gong Jun is a Chinese actor. He gained attention for his role in Lost Love In Times (2017), and further recognition for his roles in Begin Again (2020), and Word Of Honor.Gong Jun was born on 29 November 1992, in Chengdu, Sichuan, China. He studied art in his second year of high school.In 2021, Gong's ancient Wuxia drama Word of Honor with Zhang Zhehan was broadcast on Youku. He played Wen Ke Xing, gentle, but also a deep-minded, innocent and cruel Chief of the Ghost Valley.
